<SYNC Start=336794><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=337437><P Class=ENCC>
And that's Chandler<br>
climbing on Chandler.
<SYNC Start=341100><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=342675><P Class=ENCC>
