<SYNC Start=345576><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=346112><P Class=ENCC>
She's got quite an arm there,<br>
doesn't she? Yeah.
<SYNC Start=348910><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=349082><P Class=ENCC>
Hey, guys, come give me a hug.
<SYNC Start=352074><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=353419><P Class=ENCC>
Triplets, hug your aunt!
<SYNC Start=355148><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=359892><P Class=ENCC>
It's like hugging fresh cookies.
<SYNC Start=361917><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=362095><P Class=ENCC>
Oh, okay.
<SYNC Start=363323><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=363496><P Class=ENCC>
I'm gonna eat you!
<SYNC Start=365225><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=365832><P Class=ENCC>
So how you been, Frank?
<SYNC Start=367026><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=367200><P Class=ENCC>
Oh, good, you know. Life is all right.<br>
Just taking it day by day.
<SYNC Start=371102><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=371270><P Class=ENCC>
