<SYNC Start=376166><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=377076><P Class=ENCC>
- Oh, my God.<br>
- No, it's fine.
<SYNC Start=378668><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=378845><P Class=ENCC>
After I black out,<br>
he tries to put it back in, so..
<SYNC Start=381473><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=381981><P Class=ENCC>
"Willing to adopt triplets?" No.
<SYNC Start=385007><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=388154><P Class=ENCC>
Can I just say, I know we're doing this<br>
