<SYNC Start=415473><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=415648><P Class=ENCC>
You know, after this,<br>
we'll go back to our apartment..
<SYNC Start=418242><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=418418><P Class=ENCC>
Right, right. Yeah.
<SYNC Start=419578><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=419752><P Class=ENCC>
We could put on some music,<br>
light some candles, and then..
<SYNC Start=425156><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=425525><P Class=ENCC>
You want to say feel me up,<br>
don't you?
<SYNC Start=427618><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=427794><P Class=ENCC>
I just think it's something we should do.
<SYNC Start=429853><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=430963><P Class=ENCC>
- Hey, Charlie!<br>
- Hi.
<SYNC Start=432487><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=432665><P Class=ENCC>
- Hi.<br>
- Hey.
<SYNC Start=434462><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=434634><P Class=ENCC>
So..
<SYNC Start=435862><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=436235><P Class=ENCC>
- dreading this?<br>
- Oh, you bet.
<SYNC Start=438829><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=439572><P Class=ENCC>
So did you bring<br>
