<SYNC Start=445737><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=446412><P Class=ENCC>
Well, thanks.
<SYNC Start=448642><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=448848><P Class=ENCC>
